title: Cal Smart Lemon-Pepper Chicken Breasts with Fresh Salad
description: Inspired by the flavours of classic Greek cuisine, this lower-calorie dish pairs juicy lemon-pepper chicken with Greek-style salad and creamy tzatziki.

